{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Get your stuff that you want to take with you, and we'll build you in-- in the truck, in between the crates.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stand up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was standing just on the side of the railroad line, watching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Even if the Germans had come in at that particular time, they will say-- because fully dressed, hat on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And waiting for the time that he was called in to be built in-- into the crates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, that happened, just-- and nothing happened there particularly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he went outside the camp and was collected by a friend of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he brought them over to the place where he stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Actually, he stayed in the house next to where he had lived all his life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He brought them over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the one who also, I contacted on the, uh-- day before-- or when I went through the lines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Baynard ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Deboburg. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Um, well, I got, uh, then transferred to the Department of Public Works.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where I got a house in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed there from the 1st of April 1946 until um, July-- no, the 25th of October, 1955.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the date we left for Australia. '55.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, that was not particularly [? on. ?] Um, Australia right after the war-- the first thing-- when that, uh, officer, Officer [INAUDIBLE], asked me to take over the camp also for these, uh, [? christenings, ?] and I refused, I said, I want to do one thing.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to go to Indonesia to help to liberate my parents, from whom I haven't heard anything either.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, uh, he took care of that, that I could go over, um, to Indonesia.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
